Ici la libraiie au format armhf obtenue de a maniere suivante : 

1- download raspbian :

stef@raspberrypi:~/git/rt-tests $ uname -a

Linux raspberrypi 5.10.63-v7+ #1488 SMP Thu Nov 18 16:14:44 GMT 2021 armv7l GNU/Linux

stef@raspberrypi:~/git/rt-tests $ cat /etc/os-release 

PRETTY_NAME="Raspbian GNU/Linux 11 (bullseye)"
NAME="Raspbian GNU/Linux"
VERSION_ID="11"
VERSION="11 (bullseye)"
VERSION_CODENAME=bullseye
ID=raspbian
ID_LIKE=debian
HOME_URL="http://www.raspbian.org/"
SUPPORT_URL="http://www.raspbian.org/RaspbianForums"
BUG_REPORT_URL="http://www.raspbian.org/RaspbianBugs"

2- sudo apt install ncurses*

3- liste des librairies :

stef@raspberrypi:~/git/rt-tests $ ls -l /usr/lib/arm-linux-gnueabihf/*ncurses*
